      "description": "Visual diagram for Context-Free Language Closure Properties",
      "type": "animated-svg",
      "file": "../../../assets/TOC_closure-properties-cfl.svg",
      "animated": false,
      "svgContent": "<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"420\" height=\"350\" viewBox=\"0 0 420 350\"><defs><linearGradient id=\"bg\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"0%\" y2=\"100%\"><stop offset=\"0%\" style=\"stop-color:#E3F2FD\"/><stop offset=\"100%\" style=\"stop-color:#BBDEFB\"/></linearGradient><marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\"><polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#1565C0\"/></marker></defs><rect width=\"420\" height=\"350\" fill=\"url(#bg)\" rx=\"12\"></rect><text x=\"210\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    Closure Properties of Context-Free Languages\n    \n  </text><!-- Union Property --><rect x=\"50\" y=\"50\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2196F3\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"110\" y=\"75\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L₁ ∪ L₂\n    \n  </text><!-- Concatenation Property --><rect x=\"50\" y=\"110\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2196F3\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"110\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L₁L₂\n    \n  </text><!-- Kleene Star Property --><rect x=\"50\" y=\"170\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#2196F3\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"110\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L*\n    \n  </text><!-- Intersection Property --><rect x=\"250\" y=\"50\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#64B5F6\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"310\" y=\"75\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L₁ ∩ L₂\n    \n  </text><!-- Complement Property --><rect x=\"250\" y=\"110\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#64B5F6\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"310\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L Complement\n    \n  </text><!-- Difference Property --><rect x=\"250\" y=\"170\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#64B5F6\" rx=\"5\"></rect><text x=\"310\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">\n    L₁ - L₂\n    \n  </text><!-- Arrow from Closed to Not Closed --><path d=\"M210 220 Q210 250 210 270\" stroke=\"#1565C0\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\" fill=\"none\"></path><!-- Closed Label --><text x=\"110\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1565C0\" font-weight=\"bold\">\n    Closed Under\n    \n  </text><!-- Not Closed Label --><text x=\"310\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#1565C0\" font-weight=\"bold\">\n    Not Closed Under\n    \n  </text><!-- Legend --><rect x=\"50\" y=\"280\" width=\"320\" height=\"50\" fill=\"white\" rx=\"5\" stroke=\"#BBDEFB\" stroke-width=\"2\"></rect><text x=\"210\" y=\"295\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    Context-Free Languages\n    \n  </text><text x=\"210\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    are closed under union, concatenation, and Kleene star\n    \n  </text><text x=\"210\" y=\"330\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Arial\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1565C0\">\n    but not under intersection, complement, or difference\n    \n  </text></svg>",
